      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;summary&#34;&gt;Summary&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this session, we delve into the importance of effective data visualization and its role as a method for conveying information. Participants will learn about the essential ingredients of impactful visualizations and how these can be applied to policy analysis and communication.&lt;/p&gt;
